#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn35.128"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.128:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.128:0.2"
msgid "13. Gahapativagga "
msgstr "13. Householders "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn35.128:0.3"
msgid "128. Soṇasutta "
msgstr "128. With Soṇa "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn35.128:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrels’ feeding ground. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.128:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho soṇo gahapatiputto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho soṇo gahapatiputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the householder Soṇa went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.128:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme no parinibbāyanti? "
msgstr "“What is the cause, sir, what is the reason why some sentient beings aren’t fully extinguished in the present life? "

msgctxt "sn35.128:1.4"
msgid "Ko pana, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme parinibbāyantī”ti? "
msgstr "What is the cause, sir, what is the reason why some sentient beings are fully extinguished in the present life?” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.128:1.5"
msgid "(Yathā purimasuttantaṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.) "
msgstr "(This should be told in full as in SN 35.118.) "

msgctxt "sn35.128:1.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, soṇa, hetu, ayaṃ paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme parinibbāyantīti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.128:1.7"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
